        <section class="col8 body"><h1>§ 31–2501.01. Short title.</h1> <section class="content"><section><section class="line-group primary-content"><p>This chapter shall be known as the “Fire and Casualty Act.”</p></section><br/><section class="line-group annotations"><p>
      (<a class="internal-link" href="/dc/council/code/sections/31-2502.01">Oct. 9, 1940, 54 Stat. 1063, ch. 792, ch. I, § 1</a>.)
    </p><h4>Prior Codifications</h4><p>1981 Ed., § 35-1501.</p><p>1973 Ed., § 35-1301.</p><h4>Section References</h4><p>This section is referenced in § <a class="internal-link" href="/dc/council/code/sections/31-5031.01">31-5031.01</a>, § <a class="internal-link" href="/dc/council/code/sections/31-5031.02">31-5031.02</a>, and § <a class="internal-link" href="/dc/council/code/sections/31-5031.24">31-5031.24</a>.</p></section></section></section></section>
